  "summary": "bzfs is a CLI built for highly reliable and scalable near real-time ZFS snapshot replication with minimal operational complexity. It reliably replicates ZFS datasets in parallel using zfs send/receive and ssh, and can operate at sub-second intervals across large fleets of hosts. It safely supports disaster recovery and high availability (DR/HA), scale-out deployments, and protection against data loss or ransomware.",
